      "writtenOn": "2017-11-08T23:11:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think this package organization will not be sustainable. We\u0027ll have giant \u0027database\u0027 package with everything.\n\nConsider dedicating \u0027database\u0027 only to establishing *sql.DB instance, and move datacenters stuff to another package dedicated to the datacenters e.g. \u0027model/datacenters\u0027.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 15,
        "startChar": 8,
        "endLine": 15,
        "endChar": 16
      },
      "revId": "f6c8f6a7d0aadbc712cdbecbfb3a91aedc0fc2f7",
